---
source: crates/runtime/tests/search/mod.rs
description: "SELECT id, answer FROM vector_search(qs, 'second', answer) order by score desc, id LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).answer                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |   Sort: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=4                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |     TableScan: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer) projection=[id, answer, score]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@1 as answer]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[score@2 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[false]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=1000), expr=[score@2 DESC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[false]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@1 as answer, 1 - cosine_distance([-0.04382492, 0.19985613, -0.068377905, 0.40905398, 0.1309431, 0.21702312, 0.0642606, -0.18392453, 0.12284972, -0.06828425, -0.0779716, 0.056778718, -0.07829621, 0.10319664, -0.11197651, 0.11039854, 0.09313049, -0.070061915, 0.12786311, -0.20297198, -0.31963778, 0.19160584, -0.04126136, -0.12979488, -0.21349913, 0.014369582, 0.16109905, 0.07963909, -0.059627373, 0.09248168, 0.08046214, -0.08955392, -0.05280622, -0.00020613502, 0.09901353, -0.00047575484, 0.00530375, -0.008682349, 0.1454975, -0.032802712, 0.03310448, 0.070386834, 0.021913093, -0.09729417, 0.05027146, 0.0089793345, 0.22016789, -0.06972855, 0.039434433, -0.009187016, 0.12028582, -0.14222503, 0.19971755, 0.0038485164, 0.051273923, 0.090958565, -0.027466344, -0.12448798, -0.15614094, -0.09367188, 0.072442465, 0.055005666, 0.11039197, -0.12741841], CAST(answer_embedding@2 AS List(Field { name: "item", data_type: Float32, nullable: true, dict_id: 0, dict_is_ordered: false, metadata: {} }))) as score] |
|               |         SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |           CayenneAccelerationExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |             BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |               DataSourceExec: file_groups={1 group: [[<NORMALIZED_PATH>/.vortex]]}, projection=[id, answer, answer_embedding], file_type=vortex                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
